
## OIL COOLER REMOVAL/INSTALLATION  


1. Disconnect the negative battery cable.  
2. Drain the engine coolant. (Refer to 01-12 ENGINE COOLANT REPLACEMENT.)  
3. Remove the intake manifold bracket.  
4. Remove the oil filter. (Refer to 01-11 OIL FILTER REPLACEMENT.)  
5. Remove in the order indicated in the table.  
6. Install in the reverse order of removal.  
7. Inspect the engine oil level. (Refer to 01-11 ENGINE OIL LEVEL INSPECTION.)  
8. Start the engine and inspect for the engine oil leakage.  

